The Bruise is a home for short stories and essays. Words and thoughts about falling down, and getting up again.

All content by Jonathan Souder ([@blindeinstein](http://twitter.com/blindeinstein)) unless otherwise specified.
Think you have something you would like to contribute? Just want to say hi? [Contact](http://thebruise.net/contact) us.

And hey,
Thanks.
